  "2115390": {
    "name": "Project Unknown",
    "steam_appid": 2115390,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为 Paranormal Property Solutions (P.P.S.) 的天才成员，您将处理陷入困境的客户的要求，并驱除困扰他们打折房产的恶灵。在帮助客户出售无鬼房屋并确保自己应得的份额时，请务必小心谨慎！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >面对 <strong>未知</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在生存的同时，应对各种超自然现象，这些现象正在导致房产价格暴跌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/4518ed7f9f87d87c4cd6fb8267ca8ddf.poster.avif?t=1760148017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/4518ed7f9f87d87c4cd6fb8267ca8ddf.webm?t=1760148017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/4518ed7f9f87d87c4cd6fb8267ca8ddf.mp4?t=1760148017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >驱除 <strong>鬼魂</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好准备，与许多鬼魂进行令人不寒而栗的遭遇，每个鬼魂都具有独特而可怕的外观。了解有关它们的模式的更多信息，并在您值得信赖的日记中写下它们的行为，以学习如何生存。找到他们存放诅咒的物品是驱魔的关键，但活着出来也是关键！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/a15479c9a822b87e7326587b3bab71cb.poster.avif?t=1760148017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/a15479c9a822b87e7326587b3bab71cb.webm?t=1760148017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/a15479c9a822b87e7326587b3bab71cb.mp4?t=1760148017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗</strong><br>幽灵不喜欢光，所以你只能在任何时候打开有限数量的灯，否则可能会跳闸。然而，这些鬼屋里的黑暗与你习惯的黑暗不同。不惜一切代价避免它！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>瘴气</strong><br>反击蔓延在每个客户家中的侵入现象并净化它。让它变得太失控，满足要求可能就是徒劳的！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用你的<strong>特殊能力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识一群具有不同特征、个性和能力的角色。在勇气、好奇心和对真理的不懈追求的引领下，每个成员都有自己独特的能力来帮助他们克服未来的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/baa7706a553148a516131b701d3c26ac.poster.avif?t=1760148017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/baa7706a553148a516131b701d3c26ac.webm?t=1760148017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/baa7706a553148a516131b701d3c26ac.mp4?t=1760148017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Eirene</i></strong> 是一位高手塔罗牌手，她用她的牌来决定她和队友之间的命运</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Zay</i></strong> 是一名古怪的学生，他后悔加入了这支队伍，但他的狗肯定不会后悔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Luther</i></strong> 不仅是一位虔诚的牧师，他还是一名职业游戏玩家。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Nyx</i></strong> 是一名神秘学爱好者，得到了一本栩栩如生的魔法书。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >购买并使用<strong>工具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从充满神秘色彩的古代文物到最先进的鬼魂探测设备，用这些视觉上迷人的工具武装自己，将功能性与美学吸引力完美融合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/324f6d3bd847c77b78bd6b55f07ba34a.poster.avif?t=1760148017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/324f6d3bd847c77b78bd6b55f07ba34a.webm?t=1760148017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/324f6d3bd847c77b78bd6b55f07ba34a.mp4?t=1760148017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得一系列专业工具，以帮助您满足客户的要求，例如鬼魂放大镜、仪式铃、诅咒传感器和手电筒装置。明智地使用它们来穿越威胁并完成驱魔。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索闹鬼的<strong>地点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在精心设计和氛围浓厚的环境中。探索闹鬼的房子、阴森的景观和令人毛骨悚然的地点，这些都会增强恐惧感和期待感。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/5ed753ede86b7e257cde4ded50cbd284.poster.avif?t=1760148017\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/5ed753ede86b7e257cde4ded50cbd284.webm?t=1760148017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115390/extras/5ed753ede86b7e257cde4ded50cbd284.mp4?t=1760148017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在有限的灯光下，探索黑暗的氛围，寻找完成驱魔的线索。一定要小心拐角处可能出现的东西。</p>",
